body.name: SILKYDRY 4 Tier Ladder Bookshelf, Leaning Plants Display Shelf, Modern Wooden Decor Bookcase, Free Standing Shelves for Living Room Bedroom Furniture Office Bathroom Organizer (1, White)
features: 📚[Unique Ladder Shelf Bookcase]: Enhance the contemporary elegance of your home office with our stylish ladder shelving unit. Its distinctive construction, from narrow to wide, creates a layered look at organizing items, while its refined appearance blends seamlessly with any room decor. Perfect for bedroom, living room, kitchen, bathroom, office and hallway.

🌻[4-Level Leaning Ladder Rack]: Our compact ladder shelf measures 20" (L) x 18.5" (W) x 56" (H) and is the ideal storage solution for small spaces. Its innovative design maximizes vertical space while minimizing floor footprint. Four ample storage shelves in varying sizes accommodate books, photos, plants, kitchen essentials, decor, and more.

🦕[Rugged & Stable Structure]: Built with premium P2 grade particleboard, this leaning bookcase boasts waterproof and wear-resistant qualities, ensuring its durability for years to come. Its A-shaped ladder-like design creates a stable triangular frame on the side of the shelf, while the staggered cross-shaped back support adds extra stability and prevents items from sliding off.

🌵[Multi-functional Decor Bookshelf]: The layered and open shelves are easily accessible and provide the perfect finishing touch to any room. This versatile 4-tier ladder bookshelf can function as a room divider, balcony planter rack, bedroom storage solution, kitchen utensil organizer, bathroom shelving unit and living room display shelf.

🎴[Easy Installation & After-Sales Guarantee]: Just follow the numbered components and clear instructions, and with a little dedication and time, you'll have a stunning bookshelf in no time! Open shelves with smooth surfaces make cleaning a breeze. At SILKYDRY, customer satisfaction is our concern. If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us.
body.description: Description:Want to add some style and depth to your room? Need a functional display for your plants, crafts, books, spices, or dolls? Our SILKYDRY 4 Tiered Ladder Bookshelf is the solution you've been looking for.This space-saving bookshelf has 4 shelves that are narrow tops and wide bottoms for easy layering of items. Made of high-quality MDF that is durable and stable, the right-angle triangle structure on the sides of the leaning book shelf provides excellent support, while the two crossed back supports help to prevent items from falling off and also enhance its stability. The open shelves provide easy access to your items and make cleaning a breeze. The multi-functional bookshelf can be used as a room divider, plant rack, bedroom display stand, or a kitchen shelf.Features:4 tiered shelf bookcase for ample storage space.Made of premium MDF that is solid and stable.A ladder structure, combining simplicity and style for a layered effect.2 criss-crossed back bars add stability and prevent items from falling.Space-saving bookshelf for dorms and small rooms.Open shelves for easy access to everyday items and cleaning.A display stand, a room divider, a plant rack and a decorative shelf.Suitable for bedroom, balcony, living room, kitchen, bathroom office.Clear step-by-step instructions to simplify installation.Specification:Color: Black, WhiteMaterial: MDFOverall Dimension: 20’’ x 18.5’’ x 56’’ (L x W x H)Distance Between Each Shelf: 12.5” - 13.5”Loading Capacity of Each Shelf: 22 lbsPackage includes：1 x 4 Tier Ladder Shelf1 x User’s ManualWhy You Choose Our Ladder Shelf Bookcase?√ Unique trapezoidal structure saves space and brings a layered look to your room.√ Open layered shelves for easy access to daily items and cleaning.√ High-quality materials ensure long-term use of the bookshelf.
